{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make Covid-19 vaccination passports a requirement for all crowded events/venues",
        "additional_details": "I feel very strongly that if people don\u2019t get vaccinated that they shouldn\u2019t be able to mix openly where lots of people gather, where they could spread the virus. Especially with the variants, even people who are vaccinated can still get ill and die. This measure would encourage people to do the right thing and get vaccinated.",
        "background": "I would like Government to make it a legal requirement for everyone to have to show a Covid-19 vaccine passport, with a photo, in order to access pubs, clubs, sports and music events or anywhere else where lots of people gather.",
